data.title: NorthWest Arkansas Community College
data.text:
President and Dean's Lists

Students are named on the President and Dean's Lists when they achieve exceptional grade point averages.

The President's List includes student who have achieved a grade point average between 3.9 and 4.0 while enrolled for 12 or more hours.

The Dean's List includes students who have earned between a 3.5 and a 4.0 on at least 6 (six) credit hours in an academic term.

Spring 2024
